snippet.textDisplay:
I'm not punjabi by birth but I've spent about a decade in Chandigarh and it's impossible not to be captivated by rich heritage of this blessed land punjab . I was born in Kashmir , I once talking to my a friend of mine about love / heritage/cultures and traditions , I remember telling him " everyone loves kashmir that's a fact but I think God loves punjab " 
It's just a emotion that came out . 
There is something about punjabi songs that I keep coming here at 1 am . Love from kashmir
